description:
Scientists are concerned about the Petermann glacier in Greenland. Some bloggers are not. Looking at satellite photos, the bloggers seem to be right. Could this be a first?

The charity I strongly endorse is called Health in Harmony. 
   Listen to my radio report here: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b08hnly0
   Or read about it here: https://psmag.com/social-justice/save-the-trees-well-save-your-life-46121... for an explanation of their work.

  You can make a donation by bank transfer here…
https://healthinharmony.org/donate/

Or by Paypal here:
https://www.paypal.com/fundraiser/112574644767835624/charity/171300

Thanks -- Your generous donations are what keep this channel going.
